## §3 — The Sweet Sixteen — Full Content

### Initiative #1 — Let's Make Dinner
**Crown:** Maneet Chauhan — Grand Chef Mentor
**Crown letter file:** `CROWN_LETTER_MANEET_CHAUHAN-02.md`
**Category:** Food / Meal Services
**Description:** Local cooperative meal preparation and delivery. Members can order meals prepared
by local member-creators (home cooks, professional chefs). Creators keep 83.3% of earnings.
Serves the food-security mission by making quality home cooking accessible and compensating cooks fairly.
**Sub-systems:** Composes with Let's Get Groceries (ingredient sourcing) and The Family Table (family dining)
**Status:** Crown letter written; initiative fully designed

---

### Initiative #2 — Let's Get Groceries
**Crown:** (Per letters registry — José Andrés referenced as "food sourcing" Crown)
**Crown letter file:** `CROWN_LETTER_JOSE_ANDRES.md`
**Category:** Food / Supply Chain
**Description:** Cooperative grocery sourcing and delivery. Connects member-consumers to
local/regional food producers. Composes with Let's Make Dinner and The Family Table to
form the full food ecosystem.
**Sub-systems:** Food supply chain; local farmer integration
**Status:** Crown letter written; Sal Khan letter references José Andrés for Let's Get Groceries

---

### Initiative #3 — Let's Go Shopping
**Crown:** Mary Beth Laughton — Merchant Mentor
**Crown letter file:** `CROWN_LETTER_MARY_BETH_LAUGHTON-02.md`
**Category:** Retail / Cooperative Commerce
**Description:** Cooperative buying platform. Members shop cooperatively, driving fair pricing.
Merchant-creators sell through the platform keeping 83.3%. Removes extractive middlemen.
**Status:** Crown letter written

---

### Initiative #4 — Household Concierge
**Crown:** Marie Kondo (per Master Letter Registry)
**Crown letter file:** `CROWN_LETTER_MARIE_KONDO-01.md`
**Category:** Home Services
**Description:** Cooperative household services marketplace. Member-workers provide cleaning,
organizing, home repair, and maintenance services. Workers keep 83.3%.
**Status:** Crown letter written

