### Initiative #6 — Tatiana Schlossberg Health Accords
**Crown:** Alex Oshmyansky — Apothecary Mentor, Lord Banyan of The Tatiana Schlossberg Health Accords
**Crown letter file:** `CROWN_LETTER_ALEX_OSHMYANSKY_V03.md`
**Category:** Healthcare / Medication Access
**Former name:** LifeLine Medications (renamed in honor of Tatiana Schlossberg)
**Description (from crown letter verbatim):**
> "The Tatiana Schlossberg Health Accords" — healthcare access initiative. Provides affordable
> medications and health resources to members. Operates as a cooperative pharmaceutical access
> program. Composes with VSL (microfinance) and Let's Make Dinner (nutrition).
**Statutes Ward cross-reference:** Health-Accords-relevant statutes auto-flagged per jurisdiction
**Status:** Crown letter written (v03); initiative fully documented

