### Initiative #7 — MSA
**Crown:** Cathie Mahon — Treasury Keeper (per liana-banyan-context.mdc VSL Crown mapping — NOTE: registry shows some conflict; see §4)
**Category:** Financial Services / Mutual Savings
**Description:** MSA = Mutual Savings Account (inferred from context). Cooperative savings
mechanism for members. Composes with VSL (Vouched Short Loans) as the savings ↔ lending pair.
**Gap:** Limited standalone documentation found. Full description needs extraction from financial-architecture docs.
