### Initiative #13 — JukeBox
**Crown:** Taylor Swift
**Crown letter file:** `CROWN_LETTER_TAYLOR_SWIFT-02.md`
**Category:** Music / Entertainment / Fair Licensing
**Description (from all-letters compilation):**
