### Initiative #15 — Power to the People (Political Expedition)
**Crown:** Seeking
**Category:** Governance / Civic / Political Participation
**Description:** Political expedition campaign infrastructure — "Not left or right. A more effective team."
"By Their Fruits" accountability cross-reference (how legislators voted). Citizen-facing political
participation and accountability tools.
**Sub-system: STATUTES WARD** (LB-CODEX-0210, BP035 Founder direct ratification)
> *"Did I mention including a law library for everyone in the world specific to their area —
> wherever they live? It will be known as the STATUTES ward."* — Founder direct, BP035
Statutes Ward provides per-jurisdiction statute lookup, plain-language summaries, member-relevance
flags, cross-initiative compliance, and By-Their-Fruits accountability cross-reference.
**Canon Eblet:** `CANON_STATUTES_WARD_SUB_INITIATIVE_15_POWER_TO_THE_PEOPLE_LB_CODEX_0210_BP035.md`
**Status:** Crown seeking; Statutes Ward sub-system fully canonized (LB-CODEX-0210)

